coolness-enhancer
=================

coolness-enhancer helps your project stay as cool as possible by
keeping your numbers as up-to-date as possible.

How to use
----------

1.  Open a terminal and switch to the directory of a git repository.
2.  Make sure you are on the branch you want to watch for changes.
3.  Execute `enhance-coolness`.
4.  Observe as the coolness is automatically enhanced whenever a new
    commit becomes available.
